	     <tr><td valign=top id=fs8 class=mform><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=232733><span id= >DireAngel</span></a><br><span id=notbold>72 posts<br><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Good [4.30]</td><td valign=top class=mform width=100%><p>I'm surprised they haven't snuck a recommend level on this yet. You think that's nice, I quested mine, then a week later a cleric traded me a Cloak of Greater Pernicity for my CoTW..straight deal. ~BTW if anyone is Questing this, I thought I might drop a tip. Pages seem to be random drop of various mobs in First tier planes but if you want a good camp spot, try your hand at the 1 non-summoning pusling shelter in the Plane of Disease. The shelter (root looking building)that's closest to the flies has 6 &quot;a Foul Pusling&quot; in them. They don't cast, don't summon and don't have high resists or noticably high hp totals. DO NOT attack other shelters, mobs there are SK's, will HT, cast and summon the hella out of you. Puslings tend to drop Pages of Dark power rather consistantly, although sometimes they don't drop for awhile. If this hasn't caught your interest, then know that they are the best trivial loot mob in PoD hands down. They drop Tainted Planar Essence (1.5pp per) Inky Secretion (sell in bazaar for 15pp per) Vendor tropies around 20 plat, Diamonds, Raw Diamonds, and even Blue diamonds often enough to learn to love this spot during your high 50's. Mob level is 55-57 I believe. Good hunting =D<br><br>Impresario Malorian Harmonybinder,<br>65 Maestro, Qeynos Chapter<br>Tunare Server</p>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
